❌#5G mobile networks DO NOT spread COVID-19 ❌

Viruses can't travel on radio waves/mobile networks. 

COVID-19 is spread through respiratory droplets from an infected person. People can also be infected by touching a contaminated surface and then their eyes, mouth or nose. https://t.co/er6wzjMru1
